{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3337,"text":"Thank you so much, Chris."},{"time":4552,"text":"And it's truly a great honor\nto have the opportunity"},{"time":8526,"text":"to come to this stage twice;\nI'm extremely grateful."},{"time":11554,"text":"I have been blown away by this conference,"},{"time":15112,"text":"and I want to thank all of you\nfor the many nice comments"},{"time":20804,"text":"about what I had to say the other night."},{"time":23000,"text":"And I say that sincerely,"},{"time":25899,"text":"partly because (Mock sob)"},{"time":27887,"text":"I need that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29062,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34943,"text":"Put yourselves in my position."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36888,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43440,"text":"I flew on Air Force Two for eight years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46021,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"Now I have to take off my shoes\nor boots to get on an airplane!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51388,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54117,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60589,"text":"I'll tell you one quick story"},{"time":62336,"text":"to illustrate what\nthat's been like for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65479,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":67024,"text":"It's a true story --\nevery bit of this is true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70158,"text":"Soon after Tipper and I left the --\n(Mock sob) White House --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73767,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75809,"text":"we were driving from our home\nin Nashville to a little farm we have"},{"time":80748,"text":"50 miles east of Nashville."},{"time":84000,"text":"Driving ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85514,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"I know it sounds like\na little thing to you, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90741,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96234,"text":"I looked in the rear-view mirror"},{"time":101965,"text":"and all of a sudden it just hit me."},{"time":105195,"text":"There was no motorcade back there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106855,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109533,"text":"You've heard of phantom limb pain?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111550,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116386,"text":"This was a rented Ford Taurus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120626,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123154,"text":"It was dinnertime,"},{"time":125184,"text":"and we started looking for a place to eat."},{"time":128588,"text":"We were on I-40."},{"time":130017,"text":"We got to Exit 238, Lebanon, Tennessee."},{"time":133238,"text":"We got off the exit,\nwe found a Shoney's restaurant."},{"time":136950,"text":"Low-cost family restaurant chain,\nfor those of you who don't know it."},{"time":141877,"text":"We went in and sat down at the booth,\nand the waitress came over,"},{"time":146336,"text":"made a big commotion over Tipper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148346,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":150833,"text":"She took our order, and then went\nto the couple in the booth next to us,"},{"time":154277,"text":"and she lowered her voice so much,"},{"time":156405,"text":"I had to really strain to hear\nwhat she was saying."},{"time":159430,"text":"And she said \"Yes, that's former\nVice President Al Gore"},{"time":162133,"text":"and his wife, Tipper.\""},{"time":164000,"text":"And the man said,"},{"time":165551,"text":"\"He's come down a long way, hasn't he?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":167767,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172699,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"There's been kind\nof a series of epiphanies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180143,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181311,"text":"The very next day,\ncontinuing the totally true story,"},{"time":185000,"text":"I got on a G-V to fly to Africa\nto make a speech in Nigeria,"},{"time":191000,"text":"in the city of Lagos,\non the topic of energy."},{"time":194301,"text":"And I began the speech\nby telling them the story"},{"time":198121,"text":"of what had just happened\nthe day before in Nashville."},{"time":201196,"text":"And I told it pretty much the same way\nI've just shared it with you:"},{"time":204526,"text":"Tipper and I were driving ourselves,"},{"time":206288,"text":"Shoney's, low-cost\nfamily restaurant chain,"},{"time":208350,"text":"what the man said -- they laughed."},{"time":210703,"text":"I gave my speech, then went back\nout to the airport to fly back home."},{"time":214310,"text":"I fell asleep on the plane"},{"time":216200,"text":"until, during the middle\nof the night, we landed"},{"time":218762,"text":"on the Azores Islands for refueling."},{"time":221364,"text":"I woke up, they opened the door,\nI went out to get some fresh air,"},{"time":224500,"text":"and I looked, and there was a man\nrunning across the runway."},{"time":228000,"text":"And he was waving a piece\nof paper, and he was yelling,"},{"time":231079,"text":"\"Call Washington! Call Washington!\""},{"time":235981,"text":"And I thought to myself,\nin the middle of the night,"},{"time":238450,"text":"in the middle of the Atlantic,"},{"time":239910,"text":"what in the world could be\nwrong in Washington?"},{"time":242154,"text":"Then I remembered\nit could be a bunch of things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244439,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"But what it turned out to be,"},{"time":251951,"text":"was that my staff was extremely upset"},{"time":255286,"text":"because one of the wire services\nin Nigeria had already written a story"},{"time":261512,"text":"about my speech,"},{"time":262956,"text":"and it had already been printed in cities"},{"time":264956,"text":"all across the United States of America."},{"time":267312,"text":"It was printed in Monterey, I checked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269164,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270553,"text":"And the story began,"},{"time":273238,"text":"\"Former Vice President Al Gore\nannounced in Nigeria yesterday,\" quote:"},{"time":277555,"text":"'My wife Tipper and I have opened\na low-cost family restaurant'\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281208,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282874,"text":"\"'named Shoney's,"},{"time":284246,"text":"and we are running it ourselves.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":286069,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":289413,"text":"Before I could get back to U.S. soil,"},{"time":291595,"text":"David Letterman and Jay Leno\nhad already started in on --"},{"time":295733,"text":"one of them had me\nin a big white chef's hat,"},{"time":299000,"text":"Tipper was saying,\n\"One more burger with fries!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":301453,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302524,"text":"Three days later,"},{"time":303830,"text":"I got a nice, long, handwritten letter"},{"time":306593,"text":"from my friend and partner\nand colleague Bill Clinton, saying,"},{"time":310038,"text":"\"Congratulations\non the new restaurant, Al!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":312458,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319155,"text":"We like to celebrate\neach other's successes in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322316,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":328606,"text":"I was going to talk\nabout information ecology."},{"time":331177,"text":"But I was thinking that,"},{"time":333219,"text":"since I plan to make a lifelong habit\nof coming back to TED,"},{"time":337000,"text":"that maybe I could talk\nabout that another time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339717,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341141,"text":"Chris Anderson: It's a deal!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342562,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345212,"text":"Al Gore: I want to focus\non what many of you have said"},{"time":349754,"text":"you would like me to elaborate on:"},{"time":351644,"text":"What can you do about the climate crisis?"},{"time":356317,"text":"I want to start with a couple of --"},{"time":359680,"text":"I'm going to show some new images,"},{"time":362273,"text":"and I'm going to recapitulate\njust four or five."},{"time":368075,"text":"Now, the slide show."},{"time":369671,"text":"I update the slide show\nevery time I give it."},{"time":373000,"text":"I add new images,"},{"time":374261,"text":"because I learn more about it\nevery time I give it."},{"time":377823,"text":"It's like beach-combing, you know?"},{"time":379798,"text":"Every time the tide comes in and out,\nyou find some more shells."},{"time":383000,"text":"Just in the last two days, we got\nthe new temperature records in January."},{"time":389007,"text":"This is just for\nthe United States of America."},{"time":392041,"text":"Historical average\nfor Januarys is 31 degrees;"},{"time":394803,"text":"last month was 39.5 degrees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398932,"text":"Now, I know that you wanted some more\nbad news about the environment --"},{"time":403769,"text":"I'm kidding."},{"time":405404,"text":"But these are the recapitulation slides,"},{"time":408484,"text":"and then I'm going to go into new\nmaterial about what you can do."},{"time":411902,"text":"But I wanted to elaborate\non a couple of these."},{"time":414321,"text":"First of all, this is where\nwe're projected to go"},{"time":417656,"text":"with the U.S. contribution\nto global warming,"},{"time":419782,"text":"under business as usual."},{"time":421590,"text":"Efficiency in end-use electricity\nand end-use of all energy"},{"time":427000,"text":"is the low-hanging fruit."},{"time":428648,"text":"Efficiency and conservation --\nit's not a cost; it's a profit."},{"time":433176,"text":"The sign is wrong."},{"time":435877,"text":"It's not negative; it's positive."},{"time":438044,"text":"These are investments\nthat pay for themselves."},{"time":440908,"text":"But they are also very effective\nin deflecting our path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445620,"text":"Cars and trucks -- I talked\nabout that in the slideshow,"},{"time":449639,"text":"but I want you to put it in perspective."},{"time":452893,"text":"It's an easy, visible target of concern --"},{"time":457514,"text":"and it should be --"},{"time":459000,"text":"but there is more global warming pollution\nthat comes from buildings"},{"time":463703,"text":"than from cars and trucks."},{"time":466000,"text":"Cars and trucks are very significant,"},{"time":468665,"text":"and we have the lowest\nstandards in the world."},{"time":471274,"text":"And so we should address that.\nBut it's part of the puzzle."},{"time":474324,"text":"Other transportation efficiency\nis as important as cars and trucks."},{"time":479709,"text":"Renewables at the current levels\nof technological efficiency"},{"time":484075,"text":"can make this much difference."},{"time":485846,"text":"And with what Vinod, and John Doerr\nand others, many of you here --"},{"time":491825,"text":"there are a lot of people\ndirectly involved in this --"},{"time":494416,"text":"this wedge is going to grow\nmuch more rapidly"},{"time":496972,"text":"than the current projection shows it."},{"time":499183,"text":"Carbon Capture and Sequestration --\nthat's what CCS stands for --"},{"time":504947,"text":"is likely to become the killer app\nthat will enable us"},{"time":511786,"text":"to continue to use fossil fuels\nin a way that is safe."},{"time":519459,"text":"Not quite there yet."},{"time":520819,"text":"OK. Now, what can you do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526495,"text":"Reduce emissions in your home."},{"time":529022,"text":"Most of these expenditures\nare also profitable."},{"time":534007,"text":"Insulation, better design."},{"time":536000,"text":"Buy green electricity where you can."},{"time":539436,"text":"I mentioned automobiles -- buy a hybrid."},{"time":543270,"text":"Use light rail."},{"time":545505,"text":"Figure out some of the other options\nthat are much better."},{"time":548311,"text":"It's important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550254,"text":"Be a green consumer."},{"time":551997,"text":"You have choices with everything you buy,"},{"time":555000,"text":"between things that have a harsh effect,"},{"time":558631,"text":"or a much less harsh effect\non the global climate crisis."},{"time":564870,"text":"Consider this:"},{"time":566726,"text":"Make a decision to live\na carbon-neutral life."},{"time":570663,"text":"Those of you who are good at branding,"},{"time":573121,"text":"I'd love to get your advice and help"},{"time":575617,"text":"on how to say this in a way\nthat connects with the most people."},{"time":581719,"text":"It is easier than you think."},{"time":583724,"text":"It really is."},{"time":587223,"text":"A lot of us in here\nhave made that decision,"},{"time":590642,"text":"and it is really pretty easy."},{"time":592800,"text":"It means reduce\nyour carbon dioxide emissions"},{"time":598751,"text":"with the full range\nof choices that you make,"},{"time":601471,"text":"and then purchase or acquire offsets"},{"time":605620,"text":"for the remainder that you have not\ncompletely reduced."},{"time":608761,"text":"And what it means is elaborated\nat climatecrisis.net."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615755,"text":"There is a carbon calculator."},{"time":619501,"text":"Participant Productions convened --"},{"time":623000,"text":"with my active involvement --"},{"time":625594,"text":"the leading software writers in the world,"},{"time":628435,"text":"on this arcane science\nof carbon calculation,"},{"time":631762,"text":"to construct a consumer-friendly\ncarbon calculator."},{"time":636317,"text":"You can very precisely calculate\nwhat your CO2 emissions are,"},{"time":642550,"text":"and then you will be given\noptions to reduce."},{"time":645892,"text":"And by the time the movie\ncomes out in May,"},{"time":649113,"text":"this will be updated to 2.0,"},{"time":651000,"text":"and we will have click-through\npurchases of offsets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655000,"text":"Next, consider making\nyour business carbon-neutral."},{"time":658246,"text":"Again, some of us have done that,"},{"time":659878,"text":"and it's not as hard as you think."},{"time":663196,"text":"Integrate climate solutions\ninto all of your innovations,"},{"time":667410,"text":"whether you are from the technology,"},{"time":669347,"text":"or entertainment, or design\nand architecture community."},{"time":673000,"text":"Invest sustainably."},{"time":675067,"text":"Majora mentioned this."},{"time":677248,"text":"Listen, if you have invested money\nwith managers who you compensate"},{"time":684064,"text":"on the basis of their annual performance,"},{"time":686805,"text":"don't ever again complain\nabout quarterly report CEO management."},{"time":692807,"text":"Over time, people do\nwhat you pay them to do."},{"time":696736,"text":"And if they judge how much\nthey're going to get paid"},{"time":701453,"text":"on your capital that they've invested,"},{"time":704777,"text":"based on the short-term returns,"},{"time":706744,"text":"you're going to get short-term decisions."},{"time":710999,"text":"A lot more to be said about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712636,"text":"Become a catalyst of change."},{"time":714406,"text":"Teach others, learn about it,\ntalk about it."},{"time":719263,"text":"The movie is a movie version\nof the slideshow"},{"time":722692,"text":"I gave two nights ago,\nexcept it's a lot more entertaining."},{"time":726694,"text":"And it comes out in May."},{"time":729437,"text":"Many of you here have the opportunity\nto ensure that a lot of people see it."},{"time":735106,"text":"Consider sending somebody to Nashville."},{"time":739390,"text":"Pick well."},{"time":741381,"text":"And I am personally going to train people\nto give this slideshow --"},{"time":745851,"text":"re-purposed, with some\nof the personal stories obviously replaced"},{"time":750630,"text":"with a generic approach,"},{"time":752724,"text":"and it's not just the slides,\nit's what they mean."},{"time":755447,"text":"And it's how they link together."},{"time":757072,"text":"And so I'm going to be conducting\na course this summer"},{"time":761683,"text":"for a group of people that are\nnominated by different folks"},{"time":765542,"text":"to come and then give it en masse,"},{"time":767795,"text":"in communities all across the country,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and we're going to update the slideshow\nfor all of them every single week,"},{"time":774689,"text":"to keep it right on the cutting edge."},{"time":777744,"text":"Working with Larry Lessig, it will be,\nsomewhere in that process,"},{"time":781649,"text":"posted with tools\nand limited-use copyrights,"},{"time":786508,"text":"so that young people can remix it\nand do it in their own way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795170,"text":"Where did anybody get the idea"},{"time":796684,"text":"that you ought to stay\narm's length from politics?"},{"time":799060,"text":"It doesn't mean\nthat if you're a Republican,"},{"time":801174,"text":"that I'm trying to convince you\nto be a Democrat."},{"time":803935,"text":"We need Republicans as well."},{"time":805464,"text":"This used to be a bipartisan issue,"},{"time":807497,"text":"and I know that\nin this group it really is."},{"time":809978,"text":"Become politically active."},{"time":811554,"text":"Make our democracy work the way\nit's supposed to work."},{"time":814753,"text":"Support the idea of capping\ncarbon dioxide emissions --"},{"time":820326,"text":"global warming pollution --\nand trading it."},{"time":822365,"text":"Here's why: as long as the United States\nis out of the world system,"},{"time":827000,"text":"it's not a closed system."},{"time":828692,"text":"Once it becomes a closed system,\nwith U.S. participation,"},{"time":832763,"text":"then everybody\nwho's on a board of directors --"},{"time":835010,"text":"how many people here\nserve on the board of directors"},{"time":838023,"text":"of a corporation?"},{"time":840415,"text":"Once it's a closed system,"},{"time":841865,"text":"you will have legal liability\nif you do not urge your CEO"},{"time":848126,"text":"to get the maximum income from reducing\nand trading the carbon emissions"},{"time":852277,"text":"that can be avoided."},{"time":853610,"text":"The market will work\nto solve this problem --"},{"time":858949,"text":"if we can accomplish this."},{"time":862434,"text":"Help with the mass persuasion campaign\nthat will start this spring."},{"time":865843,"text":"We have to change the minds\nof the American people."},{"time":868375,"text":"Because presently, the politicians\ndo not have permission"},{"time":871158,"text":"to do what needs to be done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873355,"text":"And in our modern country, the role\nof logic and reason no longer includes"},{"time":878833,"text":"mediating between wealth and power\nthe way it once did."},{"time":881811,"text":"It's now repetition of short, hot-button,\n30-second, 28-second television ads."},{"time":887395,"text":"We have to buy a lot of those ads."},{"time":890221,"text":"Let's re-brand global warming,\nas many of you have suggested."},{"time":894555,"text":"I like \"climate crisis\"\ninstead of \"climate collapse,\""},{"time":897448,"text":"but again, those of you\nwho are good at branding,"},{"time":899799,"text":"I need your help on this."},{"time":901768,"text":"Somebody said the test\nwe're facing now, a scientist told me,"},{"time":905892,"text":"is whether the combination\nof an opposable thumb"},{"time":909000,"text":"and a neocortex is a viable combination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":911947,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":913825,"text":"That's really true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918160,"text":"I said the other night,\nand I'll repeat now:"},{"time":921584,"text":"this is not a political issue."},{"time":923773,"text":"Again, the Republicans here --\nthis shouldn't be partisan."},{"time":929336,"text":"You have more influence\nthan some of us who are Democrats do."},{"time":933421,"text":"This is an opportunity."},{"time":934921,"text":"Not just this, but connected\nto the ideas that are here,"},{"time":939797,"text":"to bring more coherence to them."},{"time":942495,"text":"We are one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944065,"text":"Thank you very much, I appreciate it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":946424,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}